These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, card-games, video-games
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, august, june
1. the person who's hobby is baking is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
3. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Hobby   | video-games | baking | card-games |
| Birthday    | august    | june | july |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, lily, amaryllis
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, soul, metal
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the far right##1
2. the fan of soul is in an even position##4
3. the fan of metal is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
4. the fan of soul is the fan of soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Flower       | lily | amaryllis | marigold |
| Music-Genre   | metal    | soul     | gospel        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
3 different pets are kept: frog, pony, horse
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, tiparillo, chaman
1. the owner of the frog is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
3. the owner of the pony is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Pet         | horse     | pony | frog |
| Cigar   | tiparillo | dunhill     | chaman  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, poppy, zinnia
There are 3 different nationalities: russian, british, argentine
1. the person who growspoppy is the british##1
2. the person who growsiris is the argentine##1
3. the person who growspoppy is in an even position##4
4. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Flower   | zinnia | poppy  | iris  |
| Nationality         | russian  | british | argentine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, videographer, journalist
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, tulip, poppy
1. the journalist is between the security-guard and the person who growsdaisy##2
2. the videographer is in an odd position##4
3. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Job         | security-guard   | journalist | videographer    |
| Flower   | tulip | poppy     | daisy |

