.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, white, aquamarine
3 different games are played: bridge, chess, domino
1. the person playing bridge is between the person playing chess and the person who likes apricot##2
2. the person playing domino is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing chess is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Color   | white | aquamarine | apricot |
| Game    | chess    | bridge | domino     |

