.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, scientific, epic
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, lemonade, iced-tea
1. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic   | scientific  | comedy  |
| Beverage         | iced-tea | lemonade | mirinda |

