The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, cooking, singing
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the art-deco house##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| House   | victorian    | art-deco      | tower |
| Hobby       | cooking | singing | reading   |

