2. the old-henry-smoker is the person watching western movies##1
3. the chaman-smoker is the person watching documentary movies##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Movie-Genre         | spy | documentary | western |
| Cigar   | pall-mall | chaman   | old-henry |

