.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
City: new-york, san-francisco, rome
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, game, oliveros
1. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
2. the montecristo-smoker is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
3. the person traveling to rome is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| City   | rome  | new-york | san-francisco   |
| Cigar         | game | oliveros   | montecristo |

