.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, iced-tea, 7up
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, snowmobile, tram
1. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person driving the snowmobile##2
2. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | 7up | soy-milk |
| Transport     | van    | tram  | snowmobile   |

