.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, lacrosse, skiing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: sports, crime, family
1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is in the middle##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is the person watching crime movies##1
4. the person watching sports movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Sport         | skiing | rowing   | lacrosse |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | sports | family      |

