2. the person who likes apricot is in an odd position##4
3. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
4. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Color      | apricot | chestnut | purple |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | adventure          | romance |

