.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, blood-red, azure
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, scientific, superhero
1. the person watching superhero movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
3. the person who likes azure is in an even position##4
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Color     | blood-red  | azure   | ebony |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | scientific | epic       |

 